{"tid":2019024,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"工聯會派教師梁子穎、理事長黃國競逐立法會勞工界議席 消息人士：變晒何君堯","createTime":"2020-05-16T04:03:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T04:33:36.000Z","uid":70063,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6d54cb4e40f7be9b3ca82755bb8974e7529c5179","tid":2019024,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T04:03:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%A9%A9%E5%A5%AA%E5%85%A9%E5%B8%AD-%E5%B7%A5%E8%81%AF%E6%9C%83%E6%B4%BE%E6%95%99%E5%B8%AB%E6%A2%81%E5%AD%90%E7%A9%8E-%E7%90%86%E4%BA%8B%E9%95%B7%E9%BB%83%E5%9C%8B%E6%8E%A5%E6%9B%BF%E5%8B%9E%E5%B7%A5%E7%95%8C%E8%AD%B0%E5%B8%AD-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB-%E8%AE%8A%E6%99%92%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25A9%25A9%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B8%25AD-%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%2581%25AF%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%25A9%258E-%25E7%2590%2586%25E4%25BA%258B%25E9%2595%25B7%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%258E%25A5%25E6%259B%25BF%25E5%258B%259E%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%2595%258C%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%25B8%25AD-%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB-%25E8%25AE%258A%25E6%2599%2592%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A0%25AF%2F&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BZzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=31522256\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25A9%25A9%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B8%25AD-%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%2581%25AF%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%25A9%258E-%25E7%2590%2586%25E4%25BA%258B%25E9%2595%25B7%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%258E%25A5%25E6%259B%25BF%25E5%258B%259E%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%2595%258C%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%25B8%25AD-%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB-%25E8%25AE%258A%25E6%2599%2592%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A0%25AF%2F&h=c53587dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%A9%A9%E5%A5%AA%E5%85%A9%E5%B8%AD-%E5%B7%A5%E8%81%AF%E6%9C%83%E6%B4%BE%E6%95%99%E5%B8%AB%E6%A2%81%E5%AD%90%E7%A9%8E-%E7%90%86%E4%BA%8B%E9%95%B7%E9%BB%83%E5%9C%8B%E6%8E%A5%E6%9B%BF%E5%8B%9E%E5%B7%A5%E7%95%8C%E8%AD%B0%E5%B8%AD-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB-%E8%AE%8A%E6%99%92%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF/</a><br />\n<br />\n消息人士向《立場新聞》透露，立法會勞工界議席，工聯會敲定由教師梁子穎，以及工聯會理事長黃國出選。有消息指，黃國出選是由於工聯會總部認為該黨的立法會辦公室「唔夠紅」，需要整頓。<br />\n<br />\n《立場》從工聯會內部得知，該黨已決定由梁子穎及黃國，接替陸頌雄及何啟明的議席。勞工界議席多年來都被工聯會「私有化」，被用作培育新人。根據該黨的不成文規定，勞工界議員任滿一屆後，必須轉戰地區直選。現任的何啟明將接替黃國健戰九東，陸頌雄則去向未定。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士指，黃國一直對工聯會立法會辦公室頗有微言，有說他認為辦公室內的職員「唔夠紅」，早已有意整治。消息人士認為，是次調配是工聯會總部整治立法會辦公室的一步棋。<br />\n<br />\n有熟悉工聯會的政圈中人慨嘆，該黨雖是「紅」，但過往仍會在民生議題上踏實處理，擔心未來工聯會會越來越不理性，「變晒何君堯」。<br />\n<br />\n現屆立法會，工聯會有五個議席，包括新界西麥美娟、港島郭偉強、九龍東黃國健，以及勞工界陸頌雄及何啟明。據了解，其中麥美娟、郭偉強及何啟明均已獲准繼續參選。<br />\n<br />\n梁子穎則曾任多年葵青區議員，亦曾任聖公會林護紀念中學教師。傘運期間，他曾撕走學生所貼傳單而遭投訴。"},{"pid":"a74966a37c983987820b2338efba8fe3c5497dfb","tid":2019024,"uid":62226,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T04:06:31.000Z","msg":"陸頌雄會去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔信佢好努力做爛仔同鬥紅都冇好位俾佢"},{"pid":"ea34d20ac5ba20ab25dacdffdee04260f3897a0e","tid":2019024,"uid":28432,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T04:09:43.000Z","msg":"現屆立法會，工聯會有五個議席，包括新界西麥美娟、港島郭偉強、九龍東黃國健，以及勞工界陸頌雄及何啟明。據了解，其中麥美娟、郭偉強及何啟明均已獲准繼續參選。<br />\n<br />\n個陣容去打MMA都得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bebfe17f2edaba8e4ec175e2d016c8adae119f54","tid":2019024,"uid":157330,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a74966a37c983987820b2338efba8fe3c5497dfb","tid":2019024,"uid":62226,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T04:06:31.000Z","msg":"陸頌雄會去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔信佢好努力做爛仔同鬥紅都冇好位俾佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T04:10:22.000Z","msg":"工聯會勞工界議員最多做1任，唔去直選就收皮"},{"pid":"be1b96f88ae8294a55392d4f07e53bb0a1e6fc77","tid":2019024,"uid":64874,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a74966a37c983987820b2338efba8fe3c5497dfb","tid":2019024,"uid":62226,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T04:06:31.000Z","msg":"陸頌雄會去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔信佢好努力做爛仔同鬥紅都冇好位俾佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T04:16:50.000Z","msg":"鬼叫佢無鬼用連黃伯都打唔低咩？有個區議員位都仲可以r去選超區。<br />\n<br />\n遲吓王國興東方日報個專欄讓番日畀佢，等佢仲有個朵搵食。<br />\n<br />\n成個工聯會係共產黨最根正曲紅嘅組織，唔紅係得唔到黨嘅留意。之前吹陳小花選勞工界個位個班人，根本唔識工聯會。"},{"pid":"c32b20355064c077521a42512d4c2daacce8841b","tid":2019024,"uid":39974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T04:19:07.000Z","msg":"一定要鬥紅"},{"pid":"dfcc88bf774c0d5e4de0aaf5d20478ce8a6d057e","tid":2019024,"uid":355793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T04:19:27.000Z","msg":"何啟明已經開始喺九龍東派傳單喇"},{"pid":"c54d4424d6de45cc0466bf7179c568435be31d7a","tid":2019024,"uid":72232,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"dfcc88bf774c0d5e4de0aaf5d20478ce8a6d057e","tid":2019024,"uid":355793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T04:19:27.000Z","msg":"何啟明已經開始喺九龍東派傳單喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T04:25:50.000Z","msg":"岩岩屌左佢一穫"},{"pid":"e9d7bd65d93d72425ec2257c638f0fb9ba1b6cbd","tid":2019024,"uid":50972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T04:30:00.000Z","msg":"陸頌雄扮紅扮到痴線咁<br />\n都話唔夠紅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢真係陰公囉"},{"pid":"60a2ad3bd53b23147007ce6a0692620e46f8d20a","tid":2019024,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfcc88bf774c0d5e4de0aaf5d20478ce8a6d057e","tid":2019024,"